r = m/n \in \mathbb{Q}
a^r = (\sqrt[n]{a})^{m}
r
a^{r+s} = a^r a^s
r,s \in \mathbb{Q}
r = m/n
s = p/q
a^{r+s} = a^{(mq+np)/nq} = \left( \sqrt[nq]{a} \right)^{mq+np} = \left( \sqrt[nq]{a} \right)^{mq} \left( \sqrt[nq]{a} \right)^{np} = a^{mq/nq}a^{nq/np} = a^{m/n}a^{q/p} = a^ra^s
